item.title: CVE-2021-24835|2024-08-03T19:42:17.420Z -- unknown -- wcfm%20%E2%80%93%20frontend%20manager%20for%20woocommerce%20along%20with%20bookings%20subscription%20listings%20compatible
item.description: The WCFM – Frontend Manager for WooCommerce along with Bookings Subscription Listings Compatible WordPress plugin before 6.5.12, when used in combination with another WCFM - WooCommerce Multivendor plugin such as WCFM - WooCommerce Multivendor Marketplace, does not escape the withdrawal_vendor parameter before using it in a SQL statement, allowing low privilege users such as Subscribers to perform SQL injection attacks
